Table of Contents¶

  • Introduction
  • Data Wrangling
  • Exploratory Data Analysis
  • Conclusions

Introduction¶

This project is gotten from a dataset with includes 24326 houses information in Nigeria. This data is based on Number of Bedrooms, Bathrooms, Toilets & Parking Space of each house, The title of the house, the town, state and price of the houses. Our Focus is going to be on The most Expensive Terraced Duplexes in Abuja and the Average Terraced Duplexes in Abuja. as it is discovered that there are houses in abuja which are expensive but have exactly the same properties with an average house in Abuja and they are both on developed towns in Abuja. So at the end of this project, we should be able to find out those houses in developed places that are expensive and also average in price and the numbers of bedrooms which they have.

Question 1 of this project is to show the location of expensive terraced duplexes in Abuja and the numbers of bedrooms available.¶
Question 2 of this project is to show the location of average terraced duplexes in Abuja, the numbers of bedrooms and the numbers of toilets available.¶

Dealing with outliers¶

In [12]:
#Using inter-quartile rqnge to take out the outliners

for x in ['price']:
    q75,q25 = np.percentile(df.loc[:,x],[75,25])
    intr_qr = q75-q25
 

    max = q75+(1.5*intr_qr)
    min = q25-(1.5*intr_qr)
 
    df.loc[df[x] < min,x] = np.nan
    df.loc[df[x] > max,x] = np.nan

# Function to find percentage between two columns grouped by one column

def percent(dframe, column1, column2):
    percentage = 'percentage'
    p = round(dframe.groupby(column1)[column2].sum(), 2).to_frame()
    p[percentage] = round((p[column2]/dframe[column2].sum())*100, 2)
    p[percentage] = p[percentage].apply(lambda x: str(x)+ '%')
    return p

Conclusions¶

In Summary, Some Terraced duplexes in Kubwa are above 75% in price that is to say that there are expensive terraced duplex houses in Kubwa, also Kubwa still has average terraced duplex houses which are at 50% in price likewise Lugbe District.¶

This shows that not all terraced duplexes in the develped parts of are really that expensive.¶

It is also discovered that bedrooms of terraced duplexes in Kubwa are actually more in an apartment compare to wuse.¶

In general, the developed towns of Abuja do not only have terraced duplexes at higher cost, they also have average terraced duplexes at average prices which is what most clients want. so it is advisable to do proper survey of where those average terraced duplexes can be found within these towns.¶
